caption:
My name is Joel Martin Turner, not to be confused with the incredibly talented beatboxer, Joel Turner from Australia. 
My wife and I live in Portland, OR with our two beautiful terrier mixes. We dream of visiting southeast Asia sometime in the future to experience the culture and history. 
Ancient lettering has always fascinated me and when I saw that lettering was becoming more common in modern design I thought I would try my "hand" at it. I love the history of letterforms and each person's take on them. 
Every morning I make a Masala Chai from scratch as a nod to past traditions. I love the art of making a good cup of tea or coffee. That being said, sometimes I just need that average cup of joe to wake up :) #handletteredABCs_2016 #handletteredABCs #abcs_name #joelmturner_featured
